    <item>
      <title>黄金持稳，因交易员消化拜登退出美国大选的影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/gold-climbs-as-us-election-chaos-escalates-after-biden-drops-out</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们考虑总统乔·拜登结束连任竞选的决定以及这对唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫的机会意味着什么，黄金价格周一几乎没有变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/gold-climbs-as-us-election-chaos-escalates-after-biden-drops-out</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 23:03:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科技股暴跌后强势反弹，收益成为焦点：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者的目光不再局限于乔·拜登结束连任竞选，而是关注科技股财报季的开始，股市在经历了 4 月份以来最糟糕的一周后出现反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/dollar-edges-lower-following-biden-s-election-exit-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 22:55:51 GMT</pubDate>
